   has been verified on convoluted three-area system for MRDED problem,
   four-area system for MRED problem and 140-unit Korean system for ED
   problem. Test results acquired from the suggested CFCEP technique have
   been fit to that acquired from FCEP, differential evolution (DE) and
   particle swarm optimization (PSO). It has been observed from the
